# Build context lives at the project root (build context: ..)
# Exclude heavy / irrelevant dirs to keep the build fast and avoid the
# nested duplicate source tree shadowing the real package.
**/.git
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
.venv
**/.venv
build
dist
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
.coverage*
src/sdk-python
phantom-stack
